{"tid":2510888,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"AI已經可以破譯古文字","createTime":"2021-04-30T12:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:48:17.000Z","uid":121784,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6600b26ba30be58c097cdf861dc5551477a78490","tid":2510888,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.technologyreview.com/2019/07/01/65601/machine-learning-has-been-used-to-automatically-translate-long-lost-languages/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2019%2F07%2F01%2F65601%2Fmachine-learning-has-been-used-to-automatically-translate-long-lost-languages%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT4jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=0357b6bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.technologyreview.com/2019/07/01/65601/machine-learning-has-been-used-to-automatically-translate-long-lost-languages/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實同電腦翻譯技術相似。<br />\n<br />\ngoogle translate: 提供外文(材料)，然後根據資料庫儲存既規則(材料)，翻譯成中文(成果)。<br />\n<br />\n破譯古文: 提供古文(材料)，以及大量同一語系既文字(材料)，搵出兩者之間既翻譯規則(成果)。<br />\n<br />\n該文作者，提供了linear B文字為希臘語系的前設，然後將古希臘文章及linear B作輸入，電腦就成功搵到兩者之間點翻譯。<br />\n<br />\n對於更古老而未成功破譯的linear A文字，有機會可以用同一方法破解。將linear A跟唔同語系既文字，都用呢個方法搵出關係。搵到關係最大既語系，而又言之成理，就可以破解。"},{"pid":"cda00a89bbc4f27274785059dad13703d811dd78","tid":2510888,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"好簡單姐<br />\n以為可以翻譯外星文"},{"pid":"8378c1dd9b1e8ede371869ba0a11a97beaca2680","tid":2510888,"uid":315326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cda00a89bbc4f27274785059dad13703d811dd78","tid":2510888,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"好簡單姐<br />\n以為可以翻譯外星文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed9a832f8931413e19f89f356e18a7aab37b5b3","tid":2510888,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor